                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850223-43-off199 t17850223-43-crimeloc201"></join>;<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="178502230094"></xptr> I keep a house there, on the 28th of January last my property was safe, I was with the bricklayers, it was half past five, and day light; on Monday morning about a quarter past seven, I saw the tiles lay upon the parapet on the first house, and I found the whole length of the gutter was gone; I found the lead afterwards at the watch-house, which was mine.</p>
